{"tid":398882,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一齊傾下各系大學教科書／教材","createTime":"2017-09-13T13:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T16:59:21.000Z","uid":68753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad454a1f56c864ffe9a981067c3515dc3b49eaf","tid":398882,"uid":68753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n呢家好多教材電子化左，網上又好多資料搵到<br />\n相信唔少人覺得教科書買黎都on99<br />\n不過亦唔少人覺得睇書比較舒服，小弟係其中之一<br />\n<br />\n近日小弟想搵其他範疇既教科書望下 (主要係undergrad level)<br />\n不過又無咩動機買新書<br />\n一來貴；二來唔係果行，唔識揀好易中伏<br />\n<br />\n於是想開個post交流下<br />\n如果大家對人地既範疇有興趣<br />\n可以一齊傾下有邊d書，或者網站係好既，值得一睇<br />\n或者grad左有唔用既書，可以交換，清下書櫃<br />\n<br />\n先講下小弟想問既範疇：<br />\n1) statistics<br />\n2) marine biology<br />\n3) astrophysics, aerophysics<br />\n<br />\n小弟可以幫忙既範疇：醫學相關<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7694343cdb479d313707ae3164edb2ec3342d324","tid":398882,"uid":3112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:41:00.000Z","msg":"Fm year:<br />\n<br />\nCalculus: Stewart <br />\n<br />\nLinear Algebra : Lay<br />\n<br />\nPhysics : Benson"},{"pid":"ec474a0f6e19852c5259af55bfca5387519b974f","tid":398882,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n利申：中文"},{"pid":"b3adcc5527fe7914432ecc53c3fa802fda2e81e1","tid":398882,"uid":68753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Fm year:<br />\n<br />\nCalculus: Stewart <br />\n<br />\nLinear Algebra : Lay<br />\n<br />\nPhysics : Benson</blockquote><br />\nBenson係咩topics都有d咁?"},{"pid":"139de8df0edd3c77d17ac3bb2f5c89231b9c6053","tid":398882,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"wiki 有出textbook, 極簡短但方便睇<br />\n<br />\n